# Redirect the legacy sitemap URL to the real Astro-generated sitemap index.
# Google Search Console still has the old /sitemap.xml submission that cannot be
# removed; without this it 404s and returns the HTML 404 page ("Sitemap is HTML"
# / "Couldn't fetch"). A 301 here makes that submission resolve to valid XML.
/sitemap.xml   /sitemap-index.xml   301
